|utst|v400|v750|veri|vi(rg|te)|vk(40|5[0-3]|\-v)|vm40|voda|vulc|vx(52|53|60|61|70|80|81|83|85|98)|w3c(\-| )|webc|whit|wi(g |nc|nw)|wmlb|wonu|x700|yas\-|your|zeto|zte\-/i&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-title function_&quot;&gt;test&lt;/span&gt;(a.&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-title function_&quot;&gt;substr&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;,&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;));
